!theme plain
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam nodesep 200
skinparam ranksep 150

' --- STYLING ---
skinparam rectangle {
 BackgroundColor #436FB6
 FontColor white
 BorderColor #2F528F
 FontSize 14
 Padding 15
}
skinparam usecase {
 BackgroundColor #436FB6
 FontColor white
 BorderColor #2F528F
 FontSize 14
 Padding 20
}
skinparam arrow {
 Color #2F528F
 FontColor #444444
 FontSize 11
 ' This helps separate text from the line visually
 MessageAlign center 
}

' --- TOP NODES ---
rectangle \"Passenger\" as Pass
rectangle \"Driver\" as Driver
rectangle \"Admin\" as Admin
rectangle \"Google Maps API\" as Google

' --- BOTTOM NODE ---
usecase \"Real-Time Bus\nTracking System\" as System

' --- ALIGNMENT (The invisible ruler) ---
Pass -[hidden]right- Driver
Driver -[hidden]right- Admin
Admin -[hidden]right- Google

' --- DATA FLOWS ---
' We declare distinct directions to force separate lines

' Passenger Pillar
Pass --> System : \" Login Credentials\n Search Bus/Route\"
System --> Pass : \"Live Map View \nNotifications (Delay) \"

' Driver Pillar
Driver --> System : \" GPS Coordinates\n Trip Start/Stop\"
System --> Driver : \"Tracking Status \nLogin Success \"

' Admin Pillar
Admin --> System : \" Manage Fleet\n Add Routes\"
System --> Admin : \"Dashboard Reports \nSystem Logs \"

' Google Pillar
Google --> System : \" Map Tiles\n Geocoding\"
System --> Google : \"Map Request \nPolyline Data \"
